  </section>
  <section>
    <num>3</num>
    <heading>Remaining Fiscal Year 2018 unexpended revenue of $122,985,000 shall be carried over into Fiscal Year 2019 as fund balance and shall be available as set forth in the approved Fiscal Year 2019 Budget and Financial Plan.</heading>
  </section>
